OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry morning with spells of
OL,6,Fsunshine, especially near western
OL,7,Fcoasts. Turning cloudy in the
OL,8,Fafternoon with the odd shower possible
OL,9,Fin the east, staying dry towards the
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy start to the evening
OL,13,Fwith any isolated showers dying out
OL,14,Fand clear intervals developing. Dry
OL,15,Fovernight with clear spells in the
OL,16,Fwest, cloudier in east. Breezy near
OL,17,Fthe coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
