OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA dry and settled day with
OL,6,Fmostly light winds. A cloudy start to
OL,7,Fthe day but cloud soon breaking up to
OL,8,Fgive long sunny periods through the
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FHigh
OL,12,Fpressure dominates bringing a dry and
OL,13,Fsettled few days with light winds.
OL,14,FPlenty of bright and sunny spells,
OL,15,Fespecially in the west with the east
OL,16,Fcloudier at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
